description:
From the developers of the mega hit Skyline Skaters comes the newest jump craze — Airheads Jump! Get involved with the latest non-stop arcade jumping action game for free today. Once you hop, you can’t stop! 
 
Oh No! The Airheads have crashed their plane and been captured by the angry Tikis. Free them all to unlock awesome new characters, but watch out for the terrifying Tiki Titan hot on your tail. 
 
Tilt and tap your device in a jungle hop to the top! Use platforms and power ups to bounce your way through over 100 levels, including catching butterflies, smacking Tikis and freeing your fellow Airheads. 
 
>>> WHY YOU’LL LOVE AIRHEADS JUMP <<<  
 
- SUPER-EASY CONTROLS 
Just tilt and tap to boost your Airhead and build awesome combos 
 
- CRAZY POWER UPS 
Use power ups and boosts to bounce higher than ever 
 
- HOURS OF FUN 
Over 100 levels of FREE bouncing fun! 
 
- BRAGGING RIGHTS 
Get to the top of the Facebook leaderboards. Compare score with your jumper friends. 
 
- CHOOSE YOUR AIRHEAD 
Who will you be today? A vampire, a wizard or even a pirate! 
 
- BEAUTIFUL HD GRAPHICS 
Crystal clarity like you’ve never seen before 
 
A big thank you to the huge Airheads community out there! 
 
Download now to play Airheads for FREE! 
 

ABOUT US

releaseNotes:
What's up fellow Airheads? It's time for another update to keep you jumping!

• Completed all levels yet? We added new ones - and even more are coming!
• Now you can jump with iOS 8 for a whole new experience! 
• Looking for extra coins? Share your replays and scores with friends to get a boost to your coin stash!
• We added more reward options! Now you can get free diamonds every day!
• Tons of fixes and general improvements to ensure a smoother Airheads experience!
